WEBVTT

1
00:00:06.379 --> 00:00:12.029
He's such an idiot.

2
00:00:12.029 --> 00:00:14.029
Hey, are you okay?

3
00:00:14.029 --> 00:00:17.019
No, I'm not okay.

4
00:00:17.019 --> 00:00:22.179
I can't believe he's been lying to me this whole time,

5
00:00:22.179 --> 00:00:26.210
pretending to follow me just to get his hands on my company.

6
00:00:26.210 --> 00:00:34.270
Kendall, there's something you should know about Raymond.

7
00:00:34.270 --> 00:00:37.820
What? More lies?

8
00:00:37.820 --> 00:00:41.140
Yeah, I don't think I can take any more surprises.

9
00:00:41.140 --> 00:00:46.789
Raymond's told me how he feels about you.

10
00:00:46.789 --> 00:00:49.789
And I can see the jealousy in his eyes when he sees us together.

11
00:00:49.789 --> 00:00:55.759
You can't fake that.

12
00:00:55.759 --> 00:00:58.530
He loves you, Kendall.

13
00:00:58.530 --> 00:01:02.140
Truly, deeply loves you.

